              },
              {
                  "layer": 4,
                  "title": "Symbolic Pattern",
                  "tag": "Somatic Metaphor",
                  "paragraphs": [
                      "Asthma can symbolically reflect smothered voice, unprocessed grief, and a life pattern where taking up space feels unsafe.",
